          a(href='http://www.masymbol.com/', target='_blank') Masymbol Technologies
          |  Pvt Ltd Â© 2016
        // End of One Page Sidebar Footer
      // End of One Page Sidebar
      // One Page Content
      .one-page-content
        // Header
        header.header.large.header-one-page.js-header-fixed
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .row
              .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-5
                .visible-sm-block.visible-xs-block
                  // Logo Image
                  a.logo-image(href='/')
                    img.img-responsive(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/skilledtree-public/logo.png', alt='logo')
                  // End of Logo Image
              .col-md-9.col-sm-6.col-xs-7
                // Menu
                nav.right.helper
                  ul.menu.sf-menu.js-menu
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers')
                        i.fa.fa-home.fa-lg
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/introduction')
                        | Introduction
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/team') Team
                    li
                      a(a='', href='#') Members
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/employees') Employees
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/recruiter') Recruiter
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/manager') Manager
                    li
                      a(href='#') Jobs
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/Jobs') Jobs
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/resumes') Resumes
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/gamification') Gamification
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/reports') Reports
                    li
                      a.active(href='#') Branding
                      ul
                        li
                          a.active(href='/hr_managers/career') Career Page
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/companybrand') Company Branding
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/dashboard') Dashboard
                    li
                      a(href='#') Header
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/header') Header Icons
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/settings') Settings
                // End of Menu
        // End of Header
        #content
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .col-md-12
              p.category-content
                | Each company has its own career page. This career page contains all the current open jobs. The purpose of this career page is to include this link to your company website. Any candidate who comes to your company website they can apply the job from your company website and you will see resumes in SkilledTree.
            .col-md-12
              #how.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | How can I include career page in our company website?
                p.category-content
                  | In the top right header, next to your team name you will find second SkilledTree icon. Career page will be opened in the separate tab by clicking on the SkilledTree icon. Here, you will see all the open jobs of your company. And each job has apply button. 
                  br
                  | 								Copy the link of this page and send it to your technical team. They will help to attach this link in your company website.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/career.png', width='100%')
            .row
              br
              br
              br
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/career2.png', width='100%')
